		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近施法的火法时，火法生成一个<span color="#ff9999">12元元素量</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">火护罩</span><span>，</span><span color="#bfdfff">水元素</span><span>破盾最快。<br/></span><span color="#ff4c4c">防护强化：</span><span>护盾盾量x2，玩家攻击护盾会被附着</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/火深渊法师.assets/Image_13.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火法施放一个贴近地面的火团，造成<span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="436" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火法施法，召唤三个一组的灼面，灼面朝中间吐火，造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%,33.3%,16.6%</span><span>伤害，持续5次。<br/></span><span color="#ff4c4c">强攻强化：</span><span>召唤3组灼面进行攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火法传送，出现在玩家正前方，同时造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>伤害，近处受玩家攻击时概率传送远离玩家，盾破之后持续攻击有小概率闪现。<br/></span><span color="#ff4c4c">灵动强化：</span><span>闪现前后位置均造成相同伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火法施法恢复火盾，期间不断召唤火喷造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，盾生成后施放冲击波造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，若处在近处，则额外再受到</span><span color="#ff9999">133.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
