		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="420" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火护罩：<span color="#ff9999">12火</span><span>盾，击破后打断并虚弱，可伤害转化。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。本体免疫燃烧伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
